  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Addressing malnutrition in flood affected areas of Matiari district Sindh</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Based on the needs identified in the above section and the primary information collected by ACF team from district Matiari, ACF would be implementing an integrated, multisectoral project with both nutrition specific and nutrition sensitive interventions as clearly outlined in UNICEF Conceptual Framework of Malnutrition and Lancet 2013 framework that all three causes (basic, underlying and immediate) need to be addressed to overcome undernutrition crisis, only possible when all sectors play their part.
The integrated Nutrition, WASH and FSL program will aim to achieve the following objective: &#x201C;To address undernutrition crisis in flood-affected areas of district Matiari through nutrition-specific and nutrition sensistive interventions&#x201D;.</narrative>
  </description>
